<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Troublous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Troublous,</orth> disturbed, restless, turbulent: <cit><quote>my t. dream this night doth make me sad,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in this t. time,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 159</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in this t. world,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.5.7" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>'twill prove a t. world,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 3, 5</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>giddy</emph>). <bibl n="shak. r3 2.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 3, 5</bibl>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>